msg: PORTLETBRIDGE-51 : Added Myfaces request attributes to excluded attributes list.  One such attribute "jsf_sequence" caused Myfaces to restore the state based on the value of this attribute vs. what was in the request -- this caused the app to revert to a prior view on things like refresh.
